sequenceDiagram
    participant Operator as TrustyAI Operator
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Adapter as LMEval Adapter<br/>(Job Pod)
    participant EvalHub as EvalHub Service<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant HF as HuggingFace Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Model as Model Endpoint<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant OCI as OCI Registry<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant MLflow as MLflow Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
        Note over Operator,K8sAPI: Job Creation
        Operator->>K8sAPI: Create Job + ConfigMap<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount<br/>TLS 1.2+
        K8sAPI-->>Adapter: Pod starts<br/>ConfigMap mounted at /meta/job.json
    end

    rect rgb(255, 248, 240)
        Note over Adapter,EvalHub: Initialization
        Adapter->>Adapter: Read /meta/job.json<br/>Path validation (CWE-22)
        Adapter->>EvalHub: POST callback_url<br/>Status: INITIALIZING<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    end

    rect rgb(240, 255, 240)
        Note over Adapter,HF: Data Loading
        Adapter->>HF: GET tokenizer + datasets<br/>Auth: HF_TOKEN (Bearer)<br/>TLS 1.2+
        HF-->>Adapter: Tokenizer + benchmark data
        Adapter->>EvalHub: POST callback_url<br/>Status: LOADING_DATA
    end

    rect rgb(255, 255, 240)
        Note over Adapter,Model: Evaluation Execution
        loop For each benchmark task
            Adapter->>Model: POST /v1/completions<br/>Auth: OPENAI_API_KEY (Bearer)<br/>TLS (custom CA supported)
            Model-->>Adapter: Completions + logprobs
            Adapter->>EvalHub: POST callback_url<br/>Status: RUNNING_EVALUATION<br/>+ progress %
        end
    end

    rect rgb(248, 240, 255)
        Note over Adapter,MLflow: Result Persistence
        Adapter->>Adapter: Write results JSON<br/>to /output
        Adapter->>EvalHub: POST callback_url<br/>Status: POST_PROCESSING
        Adapter->>OCI: Push OCI artifact via skopeo<br/>Auth: Docker config<br/>TLS 1.2+
        Adapter->>EvalHub: POST callback_url<br/>Status: PERSISTING_ARTIFACTS
        Adapter->>MLflow: POST experiment run<br/>Auth: EvalHub SDK<br/>TLS
        Adapter->>EvalHub: POST callback_url<br/>Status: COMPLETED<br/>+ overall score + results
    end
